450
01:01:04,000 --> 01:01:10,000
Now let's create the FilingsRepository class.
It inherits from BaseRepository with Filing as the model type.

451
01:01:10,000 --> 01:01:16,000
We set model_class equal to Filing.
This tells the base repository which ORM model to use.

452
01:01:16,000 --> 01:01:22,000
Now the deduplication methods. These are critical for ingestion.

453
01:01:22,000 --> 01:01:28,000
get_by_hash looks up a filing by its SHA-256 content hash.
This is how we check if a filing has already been ingested.

454
01:01:28,000 --> 01:01:34,000
We use where Filing.file_hash equals the provided hash.
