457
01:01:46,000 --> 01:01:52,000
Now the filtered queries.

458
01:01:52,000 --> 01:01:58,000
get_by_ticker returns all filings for a given ticker symbol.
We convert the ticker to uppercase for consistency.

459
01:01:58,000 --> 01:02:04,000
We order by fiscal year descending so the newest filings come first.
