466
01:02:40,000 --> 01:02:46,000
We filter for active filings only and order by ticker alphabetically.
The result is a simple list of strings.

467
01:02:46,000 --> 01:02:52,000
Notice that every database operation wraps exceptions in DatabaseQueryError.
This gives us consistent error handling across the entire repository layer.

468
01:02:52,000 --> 01:02:58,000
Let me summarize the key methods.

469
01:02:58,000 --> 01:03:04,000
For deduplication, we have get_by_hash and exists_by_hash.
These prevent re-ingesting the same filing twice.

470
01:03:04,000 --> 01:03:10,000
For filtered queries, we have get_by_ticker, get_by_ticker_and_type,
